   {c - 1} &amp; {c + 1} &amp; {{{\left( { - 1} \right)}^n}c}  \cr 

 } } \right| = 0$$
<br><br>(Taking transpose of second determinant)
<br><br>$$\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,{C_1} \Leftrightarrow {C_3}$$
<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow \left| {\matrix{
