 } } \right| = 0$$
<br><br>$$\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,{C_2} \Leftrightarrow {C_3}$$
<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow \left| {\matrix{
