<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow $$ $${a_1^2 + a_2^2} $$ = $${2 \over 3}b_1^2 + {{\left( {{k^2} + 1} \right)} \over 3}b_2^2 + {2 \over 3}{b_1}{b_2}\left( {k - 1} \right)$$
